    content: `**Recommended Stone Age Build Order:**\n\n**First 5 Buildings (Ticks 1–30):**\n- Farm — Ensure food security from day one\n- Housing — Open population capacity for growth\n- School — Start Tech Point generation immediately\n- Lumberyard — Boost wood for future construction\n- Gold Mine — Improve gold income for trade/treasury\n\n**Next 5 Buildings (Ticks 30–70):**\n- Granary — Expand food storage, prevent waste\n- Barracks — Get Defense Level above 25\n- Housing (second) — Keep pace with population growth\n- Quarry — Stone becomes critical for walls and military\n- School (second) — Accelerate Tech Points for epoch advance\n\n**Bronze Age transition targets:**\n- 2+ Schools before advancing\n- At least 200 stored Tech Points\n- Housing capacity ≥ 30\n- Defense Level ≥ 30\n- Treasury ≥ 300 Credits\n\n**What NOT to build early:**\n- University (too expensive, need College first)\n- Fortress (wait for Medieval Age)\n- Factory (Industrial Age required)\n- Bank (use marketplace lending for now)`,
